record.title: THE JOURNAL
record.chair: The Chair has examined the Journal of the last day's proceedings and announces to the House her approval thereof.

speaking-unknown-id.title: Mr.
speaking-unknown-id.name: POE
speaking-unknown-id.paragraph: Madam Speaker, pursuant to clause 1, rule I, I demand a vote on agreeing to the Speaker's approval of the Journal.

record.chair: The question is on the Speaker's approval of the Journal.

speaking-unknown-id.title: Mr.
speaking-unknown-id.name: POE
speaking-unknown-id.paragraph: Madam Speaker, on that I demand the yeas and nays.

record.narrative: The yeas and nays were ordered.
record.chair: Pursuant to clause 8, rule XX, further proceedings on this question will be postponed.
